data.description: This is the home you have been looking for. Welcome to 2240 Martin Drive in Florissant MO. This 4 Bedroom 2 Full bathroom home has been completely updated and is ready for your family. Walking into the property you will immediately notice the open floorplan and the updated flooring. Walking into the kitchen you will see stainless steel appliances, newer counter tops and custom cabinets. Each of the 4 bedrooms in this home have great closet space and large windows. The lower level is finished and also has a full bathroom. Wait, there is more. Heading to the back yard you will find a bonus room with a fireplace that could make for a great home office or another place to relax. There is a new roof on the house that is less than 1 year old, the black stainless-steel appliances stay with home and all major plumbing has been updated within the last year.  Make your appointment to see this home today.
